## First-Time Setup

### 1. GitHub Authentication
```bash
gh auth login
# Select: GitHub.com
# Protocol: HTTPS
# Authenticate: with web browser
# Organization: infiquetra
```

### 2. Configure Git
```bash
git config --global user.name "{{ item.key | title }}"
git config --global user.email "{{ item.value.email }}"
git config --global init.defaultBranch main
```

### 3. Claude Code Authentication
```bash
claude-code auth
# Follow browser authentication flow
```

### 4. Watch Infiquetra Repositories
```bash
# Clone infiquetra organization repos
gh repo list infiquetra --limit 100 | while read -r repo _; do
    gh repo clone "$repo" ~/repos/
done

# Set up GitHub notifications
gh auth refresh -s notifications
```

