### 6. SSH Keys (if needed)
```bash
ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C "{{ item.value.email }}"
cat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub
# Add to GitHub: https://github.com/settings/keys
```

### 7. Verify Environment
```bash
# Check tools
claude-code --version
gh --version
python3 --version
node --version

# Check repos
ls ~/repos/
```

